stosterone\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"the blood\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the ruling, in order to compete, athletes with DSD will have to reduce their blood testosterone level to below 2.5 nanomoles per litre.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"score\": 0.9652258991951613, \"rank\": 0.036026903995993426, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ruling\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"their blood testosterone level\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"below 2.5 nanomoles\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"litre\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The previous limit had been five.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The previous limit\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes must also have a blood testosterone level below the new limit for two years before being allowed to compete in the female category of any track and field event.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"a blood testosterone level\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"the new limit\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"the female category\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"any track and field event\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For those already competing, they would have to remain under the new threshold limit for six months before being allowed to compete again.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new threshold limit\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The previous restrictions had only been in place for distances between 400m and a mile.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The previous restrictions\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"distances\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2461}, {\"ngram\": \"between 400m\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"a mile\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who are the DSD athletes?\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2500, \"end\": 2503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"score\": 0.9652258991951613, \"rank\": 0.036026903995993426, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Caster Semenyais the highest-profile DSD athlete and has refused to take the testosterone suppressors in order to compete.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"score\": 0.9652258991951613, \"rank\": 0.036026903995993426, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Caster Semenyais\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"the testosterone suppressors\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2616}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has taken her case to the European Court of Human Rights on the basis of disc